# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Usage/Behavior (Rails Infrastructure)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Template Processing:
#   - Lines starting with # are comments (removed from final message)
#   - Blank lines are preserved
#   - Subject line: 72 chars max
#   - Body lines: wrap at 72 chars
#   - Leave blank line between subject and body
#
# Keying Format:
#   [DOMAIN] TYPE: High-level description of understanding gained
#
# Types by Work Phase:
#
#   FOUNDATION (0) - Establishing anchors:
#     INIT   - Initialize new component/structure
#     SEED   - Plant crystallized understanding
#     ANCHOR - Establish fixed reference point
#
#   BUILD UP (+1) - Constructing from foundation:
#     BUILD   - Create/construct new capability
#     EXPAND  - Extend existing functionality
#     CONNECT - Link components together
#
#   BREAK DOWN (-1) - Refining toward essence:
#     REFINE  - Improve/polish existing work
#     DISTILL - Extract essential understanding
#     FIX     - Correct issues/errors
#
#   OPERATIONS - Maintenance:
#     SYNC    - Synchronize between locations
#     MIGRATE - Move/restructure content
#     CLEAN   - Remove obsolete/cleanup
#
# Versioning (Ternary - CPSI-ALG-005):
#   Format: STAGE-ITERATION.PHASE (e.g., a-03.45)
#   Stage: a=alpha, b=beta, c=complete
#   Phase ranges: 00-32=fix, 33-65=changing, 66-99=set
#
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# END SETUP
# =============================================================================

