# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TERNARY VERSIONING (CPSI-ALG-005)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Format: STAGE-ITERATION.PHASE  (e.g., a-03.45)
#
# STAGE (FIXED until transition):
#   a = Alpha (unstable, forming)
#   b = Beta (working, baseline)
#   c = Complete (stable, proven)
#
# ITERATION (CHANGES on milestone): 00-99
#   Increments when you complete a milestone
#
# PHASE (you SET): 00-99
#   00-32 = Fix range (early, seeding)
#   33-65 = Changing range (active development)
#   66-99 = Set range (nearing completion)
#
# Example progression:
#   a-00.00 → Start
#   a-01.45 → Iteration 1, actively developing
#   a-02.80 → Iteration 2, nearing complete
#   b-00.00 → Beta! It works!
#   c-00.00 → Stable release
